>\n用fake news做大外宣<br />\n只要洗到一部分人腦就會成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAh9yww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAh9yww.jpg&h=99c72eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"王太用心良苦<br />\n無忘六四呀<br />\nbtw twitter,fb應該出alert 更正呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8d40a68b4e4e69d33248b8ff37e38d0dec074f","tid":2358471,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f22be00d955bb3091c70728ee80fe2159684258","tid":2358471,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"431290d63bc8d8c2d6fbdaeb6cf7d123b2d7ee27","tid":2358471,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:08:07.000Z","msg":"黨媒又炒車"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔係炒車<br />\n全部黨媒統一口徑造假<br />\n例如CCTVB尋日同共諜港奸配合<br />\n用fake news做大外宣<br />\n只要洗到一部分人腦就會成功<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAh9yww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAh9yww.jpg&h=99c72eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"wow 有埋樣 想比我地篤灰?"},{"pid":"92f5eebc0dd5ba5f983d7a55e045be0e61a3822e","tid":2358471,"uid":288646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"2019年6月19日，佩洛西在基督科學箴言報贊助的早餐會上批評中國違反一國兩制。記者提問關於中國的香港局勢，佩洛西指「200萬人，佔全香港四分之一，上街反對引渡條例是一道美麗的風景線（a beautiful sight to behold）」[16][17][18]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/南希&middot;佩洛西\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%8D%97%E5%B8%8C%C2%B7%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=b0136e67\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/南希&middot;佩洛西</a>"}]}